---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// One standard price per the "no founder / no launch offers" standing rule (15 Jun 2026).
// Everyone pays the same standard price. No founder/launch offer. No bundle.
const tiers = [
  {
    name: 'Starter',
    sites: '1 site',
    price: 149,
    features: [
      'Unlimited affiliates',
      'All v1.1.0 features unlocked',
      'MLM / two-tier referrals',
      'AI swipe-copy generator',
      'Stripe Connect + PayPal API auto-payout',
      'Cloud-assist fraud detection',
      'EDD + Surecart adapters',
      '1 year of updates + support',
    ],
    cta: 'Get Starter',
    ctaUrl: 'https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/buy/aff-starter',
  },
  {
    name: 'Pro',
    sites: '3 sites',
    price: 299,
    highlighted: true,
    features: [
      'Everything in Starter',
      '3-site licence',
      'Priority email support',
      '1 year of updates + support',
      'Per-product commission rates',
      'A/B email testing',
      'WP-CLI commands',
      'Real-time stats REST API',
    ],
    cta: 'Get Pro',
    ctaUrl: 'https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/buy/aff-pro',
  },
  {
    name: 'Agency',
    sites: '10 sites',
    price: 549,
    features: [
      'Everything in Pro',
      '10-site licence',
      'White-label affiliate portal CSS',
      'Priority support + Slack channel',
      'Migration assistance from AffiliateWP / SliceWP',
      '1 year of updates + support',
    ],
    cta: 'Get Agency',
    ctaUrl: 'https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/buy/aff-agency',
  },
];
---

<Layout seoSlug="/pricing">
  <section class="pricing-hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">★ Annual licence · self-hosted · one standard price</div>
    <h1>Asteris Affiliates pricing — from $149/yr.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Three tiers based on site count. <strong>Starter $149/yr (1 site), Pro $299/yr (3 sites), Agency $549/yr (10 sites).</strong>
      Every feature is unlocked on every tier — the tier just changes how many activations you get. One standard price for everyone, no bundle gymnastics.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="tiers">
    <div class="tiers-grid">
      {tiers.map(t => (
        <div class:list={['tier', { highlighted: t.highlighted }]}>
          {t.highlighted && <div class="badge">MOST POPULAR</div>}
          <h2 class="tier-name">{t.name}</h2>
          <p class="tier-sites">{t.sites}</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="dollar">$</span><span class="amount">{t.price}</span>
            <span class="per">/yr</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="tier-features">
            {t.features.map(f => <li>✅ {f}</li>)}
          </ul>
          <a href={t.ctaUrl} class:list={['btn', 'btn-large', t.highlighted ? 'btn-pop' : 'btn-outline']}>
            {t.cta} →
          </a>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="renewal">
    <div class="renewal-inner">
      <h2>What happens after year 1?</h2>
      <div class="renewal-grid">
        <div class="renewal-item">
          <h3>You keep using it</h3>
          <p>Plugin keeps working forever. Last-installed-version stays active. No "killswitch" if you don't renew.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="renewal-item">
          <h3>You stop getting updates</h3>
          <p>No security patches, no new features, no support tickets. Recommended: renew before licence expires.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="renewal-item">
          <h3>Simple annual renewal</h3>
          <p>One standard price across every tier — $149 / $299 / $549 per year. No per-affiliate metering, no SaaS surcharge, no surprise add-on bills.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="value">
    <div class="value-inner">
      <h2>What every tier includes</h2>
      <p>The tier-card lists above are the marketing version. The honest answer is that all three tiers unlock every feature in the plugin — the tier just controls site count and support level. So Starter at $149/yr is the full feature set on one site; Pro and Agency add more activations plus tiered support.</p>
      <p>The full feature set, regardless of tier: unlimited affiliates per site, two-tier (MLM) referrals, AI swipe-copy generator, cloud-assist fraud detection (opt-in), Stripe Connect Express direct payouts at 0.25%, PayPal Payouts API with batch scheduling, bank-CSV export (AU + US formats), EDD adapter, Surecart adapter, custom cart adapter via Order_Source interface, vanity <code>{`/go/{handle}`}</code> landing pages with cookie + view tracking, A/B email testing on transactional emails, real-time stats REST API (cursor-paginated, transient-cached), full WP-CLI suite, per-product commission rates, admin impersonation, onboarding wizard, email throttling, mobile-responsive affiliate portal, denormalised aggregates for sub-50ms stats queries, full translation-ready (.pot included).</p>
      <p>What changes between tiers: <strong>site count</strong> (1 / 3 / 10), <strong>support tier</strong> (forum-first on Starter, priority email on Pro, priority + Slack channel on Agency), and <strong>migration assistance</strong> (DIY on Starter; we run the import for you on Pro and Agency). <a href="/modules">See all 31 modules →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="guarantee">
    <div class="guarantee-inner">
      <h2>14-day money-back guarantee</h2>
      <p>Try it for two weeks. If it doesn't replace your AffiliateWP / SliceWP / Tapfiliate install, email us — full refund, no questions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq">
    <div class="faq-inner">
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>Why just one standard price?</summary>
        <p>Because our price is already 3–9× cheaper than every competitor. A "discount" off $149/yr would be a marketing trick, not a real saving. Everyone pays the same standard price — we'd rather you trust the sticker price.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I upgrade between tiers later?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Prorated upgrade from Starter→Pro→Agency at any time. Email us with your licence key.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is there a free tier?</summary>
        <p>Yes — under 25 affiliates and no MLM / AI swipe / cloud fraud / PayPal-API features. <a href="/free">See the free tier</a>.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Does this work with EDD / Surecart / WooCommerce only?</summary>
        <p>All three. WC is native; EDD + Surecart via adapters in <code>src/Adapters/</code>. Other carts: write your own adapter against the <code>Order_Source</code> interface — single file.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Where is my data?</summary>
        <p>On your server. No SaaS, no calls to our servers (except the optional cloud-assist fraud signal sharing, which sends only SHA-256 hashes — no PII). Disable cloud-assist and there's literally zero outbound traffic.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Refund policy?</summary>
        <p>14 days, no questions asked.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .pricing-hero { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 96px 24px 48px; text-align: center; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--c-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .pricing-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .pricing-hero .lead { font-size: 18px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; }

  .tiers { padding: 32px 24px 96px; }
  .tiers-grid { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .tiers-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .tier { background: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--c-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px 32px; position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .tier .btn { margin-top: auto; }
  .tier-features { flex: 1 0 auto; }
  .tier.highlighted { border-color: var(--c-mint); box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--c-mint); }
  .badge { position: absolute; top: -14px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--c-mint); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
  .tier-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--c-muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .tier-sites { color: var(--c-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; }
  .tier-price { font-size: 56px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .tier-price .dollar { font-size: 28px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 4px; }
  .tier-price .per { font-size: 18px; color: var(--c-muted); font-weight: 600; margin-left: 4px; }
  .tier-features { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 32px; }
  .tier-features li { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border); font-size: 14px; }
  .tier-features li:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .tier .btn { width: 100%; text-align: center; }

  .renewal { background: #fff; padding: 96px 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
  .renewal-inner { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; }
  .renewal h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .renewal-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 32px; }
  .renewal-item { padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid var(--c-mint); background: var(--c-bg); border-radius: 4px; }
  .renewal-item h3 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .renewal-item p { color: var(--c-muted); line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; }

  .guarantee { padding: 64px 24px; background: var(--c-bg); text-align: center; }
  .guarantee-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .guarantee h2 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .guarantee p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.6; }

  .value { padding: 80px 24px; background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
  .value-inner { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .value h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .value p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--c-text); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .value strong { color: var(--c-text); font-weight: 700; }
  .value a { color: var(--c-mint); font-weight: 600; }
  .value code { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; }
  .faq { padding: 96px 24px; background: #fff; }
  .faq-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .faq h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); margin-bottom: 32px; text-align: center; }
  details { border: 1px solid var(--c-border); border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 16px 20px; }
  details[open] { border-color: var(--c-mint); }
  summary { font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; }
  details p { margin-top: 12px; color: var(--c-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  details a { color: var(--c-mint); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
